io.sphere.sdk.models

Interface Reference<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the referenced object
    All Superinterfaces:
    Identifiable<T>, Referenceable<T>, ResourceIdentifiable<T>, ResourceIdentifier<T>

    public interface Reference<T>
extends Referenceable<T>, Identifiable<T>, ResourceIdentifier<T>
    A Reference is a loose reference to another resource on the SPHERE.IO platform. The reference may have a copy of the referenced object available via the method getObj() For equals, only the getTypeId() and getId() are compared used and getObj() will be ignored.
